The '''International Forum of Independent Audit Regulators (IFIAR)''' was established in India in 2006 to conduct [[audit]]s of Indian businesses. It has 52 independent [[Financial audit|audit]] regulators as members.<ref>{{citation |title=What is National Financial Reporting Authority? |url=https://www.thehindu.com/business/Economy/what-is-national-financial-reporting-authority/article23280972.ece |work=[[The Hindu]] |date=17 March 2018 }}</ref>

